"<div class=\"announce instapaper_body md\" data-path=\"README.md\" id=\"file\"><article class=\"markdown-body entry-content\" itemprop=\"text\"><h1><a href=\"#metalsmith-global-metadata\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\" id=\"user-content-metalsmith-global-metadata\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>metalsmith-global-metadata</h1>\n<p>Add metadata to the Metalsmith pipeline.</p>\n<p>This adds metadata globally to Metalsmith,\nif you're looking to add metadata to individual files\nyou can use the excellent <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/metalsmith-metadata\" rel=\"nofollow\">metalsmith-metadata</a> plugin.</p>\n<h2><a href=\"#installation\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\" id=\"user-content-installation\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Installation</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-shell\"><pre>$ npm install https://github.com/gaggle/metalsmith-global-metadata.git</pre></div>\n<h2><a href=\"#usage\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\" id=\"user-content-usage\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Usage</h2>\n<p>Pass data you want to add to global metadata:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-js\"><pre><span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">metadata</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">require</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>metalsmith-global-metadata<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>);\n\n<span class=\"pl-smi\">metalsmith</span>.<span class=\"pl-en\">use</span>(<span class=\"pl-en\">metadata</span>({\n  data<span class=\"pl-k\">:</span> {foo<span class=\"pl-k\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>bar<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>},\n  pkg<span class=\"pl-k\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">require</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>./package.json<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>),\n}));</pre></div>\n</article></div>"